{"word":"κερτομέω","slug":"κερτομέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>κερτομέω</b></el> <el>(κερτομέω,) ( φυτ. <el>-ήσω</el>) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><el>κέρτομος</el>\n<p/><i>to taunt</i> or <i>sneer at</i>, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a> <a href='S:person, personal'>pers.</a>, <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>: <a href='S:absolute, absolutely'>absol.</a> <i>to sneer</i>, <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b>:— <a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to be scoffed at</i>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/>"}]}